name: Aqua Jack
overview: Aqua Jack is arcade pseudo-3D shooter, it's similar to After Burner or Bimini Run. The player controls a war hovercraft, and fights against enemy's forces - like helicopters, boats, planes, tanks etc. He has cannon with unlimited ammo, and several bombs, his vehicle has turbo mode and ability to jump. Hovercraft must avoid various obstacles (natural and enemy's water mines) and enemy bullets - it's very fragile. Game has 8 levels.
